  "interpretation": "Thermal dose is strongly correlated with EC50 in raw form but is ~0.83 collinear with elapsed time; it adds only 4.7% R2 over a plain time trend and does not track EC50's off-trend variation. With a single observational co-trending series the chronic-heat hypothesis cannot be causally separated from a shared secular trend \u2014 it is a plausible mechanism supported by physiology and by the exclusion of alternatives (Cu speciation, assay precision, nutrients), not a demonstrated one."
